WEBVTT

00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:07.000
In the Issue Reports module, we can manage sensor incidents and maintenance.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:18.000
Press New report, select the affected equipment, write a subject and description, and save.

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:27.000
The report is registered with Pending status in the history table, where you can change it to Resolved or delete it.

00:00:27.500 --> 00:00:35.000
With Register maintenance, note the equipment and the action taken to document each intervention.
